{"tid":1354283,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我宣布所有花生post討論到5點","createTime":"2019-07-23T06:11:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T06:19:38.000Z","uid":76543,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"bf434623a4cce6f0f987526a4081762567460d48","tid":1354283,"uid":76543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T06:11:47.000Z","msg":"何妖嘅post成個熱門都係<br />\n光復元朗嘅就寥寥可數 我有啲中學師弟最後連係727定728都搞唔清楚<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">點解呀</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n因為成個熱門都係推緊花生post呀<br />\n笑何妖on9我都有笑 有冇必要十幾個post呀 仲要個個都推<br />\n唔好唔記得721有開槍暴力鎮壓 又有元朗恐怖襲擊<br />\n推番啲有用post 資訊post 大家光復元朗都要和理非幫手<br />\n唔通你真係入去打仗咩<br />\n之前銀髮族幫大家出一分力 佢哋今日有上連登都唔知搵唔搵到光復元朗資訊 咁點幫手 點了解呀<br />\n琴日就上環post俾元朗post遮哂 咁都算呀 元朗恐襲都重要<br />\n咁今日呢 係不斷抽水 笑笑笑笑笑 食花生<br />\n<br />\n唔好唔記得<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>光復香港<br />\n時代革命</strong></span></span><br />\n呢一刻去哂抽水講笑 抽一陣都明 一路抽到重點都好似遮哂咁 仲對唔對得住721義士<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>唔係分化你哋<br />\n係想大家唔好俾太多嘢分散焦點</strong></span></span><br />\n大家出力推番光復元朗post 721上環post出嚟好唔好呀<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>上環暴力鎮壓<br />\n元朗恐怖襲擊</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n少開post 可能打得唔好<br />\n大家睇完認同就去推爆其他光復元朗post啦"},{"pid":"0a753e27fea645bc0549cb174c67553d71b77e75","tid":1354283,"uid":76543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T06:12:12.000Z","msg":"光復香港"},{"pid":"6942a5824cd8c517388c2b9f426fa35864337187","tid":1354283,"uid":76543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T06:12:22.000Z","msg":"時代革命"},{"pid":"3dfc6e805fef1329e9754aaeda0ed404169834ed","tid":1354283,"uid":76543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T06:13:16.000Z","msg":"唔好中共狗詭計 唔好被分焦"},{"pid":"4ddff6ccdf1d61e0178e727155eb9c3f3c7cc005","tid":1354283,"uid":76543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T06:14:55.000Z","msg":"唔好再推埋啲牛屎佬引戰啲post<br />\n負皮<br />\n上一頁<br />\nBlock柒佢<br />\n言都唔好留就得啦"},{"pid":"392b7724e33344d7b4d448c01c77314c16bc81a1","tid":1354283,"uid":76543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T06:15:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbc51fbf66b46cf8ed8c64bd855d9b34c8bf9938","tid":1354283,"uid":76543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T06:16:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e5955d52847068fd70432ed94052733c0ea1de6","tid":1354283,"uid":76543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T06:16:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c70b6782083685dd15034d676da4df526e1ee2d","tid":1354283,"uid":76543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T06:16:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2df189f2b16f87f000ae46c341fb9627da22e7f7","tid":1354283,"uid":76543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T06:16:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36adcdc55023067522bedb375a5e3071f6c925fc","tid":1354283,"uid":76543,"like":0,"disli